name: Convert to AV1
description: https://github.com/BigFlubba/Tdarr-Megaflows This flow will process any file you throw at it (movies, TV shows, normal flat videos, & even VR videos) and is designed to handle them accordingly, make backups of all files before processing in case of transcode issues, remove all close captions, extract subtitles, (for manually adding specific subtitles (like forced subtitles) remove all embedded subtitles (except burned in subtitles), automatically sort and handle files that grew or shrunk in excessive amounts, sort, & move the final file to appropriate directories. In the end, this flow will convert everything to AV1 inside an MKV container.

Big Flubba's "Convert To AV1" megaflow. | v1 | https://github.com/BigFlubba/Tdarr-Megaflows

This flow will process any file you throw at it (movies, TV shows, normal flat videos, & even VR videos) and is designed to handle them accordingly, make backups of all files before processing in case of transcode issues, remove all close captions, extract subtitles, (for manually adding specific subtitles (like forced subtitles) remove all embedded subtitles (except burned in subtitles), automatically sort and handle files that grew or shrunk in excessive amounts, sort, & move the final file to appropriate directories.
In the end, this flow will convert everything to AV1 inside an MKV container.
